#
# dockdodge - prevent apps from showing in the dock while running
# we add the following two lines (sans #) to the end of an application's
# info.plist in its .app bundle
# This is supposed to work per:
# http://www.cultofmac.com/202024/hide-the-dock-icon-for-any-running-app-os-x-tips/ 
#
# LSUIElement
#
# 1
#
sudo echo "LSUIElement" >> Info.plist
sudo echo " " >> Info.plist
sudo echo "1" >> Info.plist
